# CODEOWNERS — ClipMCP
#
# Each line maps a file pattern to one or more owners (GitHub users or teams).
# When a PR touches a matching file, the listed owners are automatically
# requested for review and their approval is required before merge
# (if "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled in branch protection).
#
# Syntax:
#   <pattern>   @<github-username-or-team>
#
# Patterns follow .gitignore rules. More specific patterns override broader ones.
# The LAST matching pattern wins.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

